{"image_id": "NVR_2005_page_16", "image_size": [1275, 1650], "ocr": [{"text": "11", "bbox": [641.0, 1549.4, 663.9, 1574.8]}, {"text": "PART II", "bbox": [587.0, 102.2, 678.6, 127.6]}, {"text": "Item 5.  Market for Registrant's Common Equity, Related Stockholder Matters and Issuer Purchases", "bbox": [135.0, 159.7, 1129.4, 185.1]}, {"text": "of Equity Securities.", "bbox": [219.4, 186.1, 423.0, 211.4]}, {"text": "Our shares of common stock are listed and principally traded on the American Stock Exchange", "bbox": [210.0, 238.6, 1087.6, 263.9]}, {"text": "(“AMEX”).  The following table sets forth the high and low closing prices per share for our common stock", "bbox": [135.0, 265.0, 1121.2, 290.3]}, {"text": "for each fiscal quarter during the years ended December 31, 2005 and 2004:", "bbox": [135.0, 291.4, 837.8, 316.7]}, {"text": "HIGH", "bbox": [735.0, 341.7, 834.0, 364.8]}, {"text": "LOW", "bbox": [903.7, 341.7, 1002.7, 364.8]}, {"text": "Prices per Share:", "bbox": [210.0, 365.7, 369.3, 388.8]}, {"text": "2005:", "bbox": [285.0, 413.5, 339.0, 436.6]}, {"text": "First Quarter      . . . . . . .", "bbox": [360.0, 437.3, 590.2, 460.4]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [716.2, 437.3, 731.9, 460.4]}, {"text": "808.00", "bbox": [752.8, 437.3, 815.3, 460.4]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [885.1, 437.3, 900.8, 460.4]}, {"text": "709.00", "bbox": [921.5, 437.3, 984.1, 460.4]}, {"text": "Second Quarter  . . . . . . .", "bbox": [360.0, 461.3, 590.4, 484.4]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [716.4, 461.3, 732.0, 484.4]}, {"text": "810.00", "bbox": [752.9, 461.3, 815.3, 484.4]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [885.1, 461.3, 900.7, 484.4]}, {"text": "712.50", "bbox": [921.5, 461.3, 984.0, 484.4]}, {"text": "Third Quarter     . . . . . . .", "bbox": [360.0, 485.1, 573.9, 508.3]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [716.1, 485.1, 731.8, 508.3]}, {"text": "938.00", "bbox": [752.7, 485.1, 815.3, 508.3]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [885.0, 485.1, 900.7, 508.3]}, {"text": "799.50", "bbox": [921.5, 485.1, 984.1, 508.3]}, {"text": "Fourth Quarter   . . . . . . .", "bbox": [360.0, 509.1, 572.9, 532.3]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [716.2, 509.1, 731.8, 532.3]}, {"text": "886.00", "bbox": [752.7, 509.1, 815.3, 532.3]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [885.1, 509.1, 900.7, 532.3]}, {"text": "660.00", "bbox": [921.5, 509.1, 984.1, 532.3]}, {"text": "2004:", "bbox": [285.0, 557.3, 339.0, 580.4]}, {"text": "First Quarter      . . . . . . .", "bbox": [360.0, 581.0, 590.1, 604.1]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [716.2, 581.0, 731.8, 604.1]}, {"text": "483.00", "bbox": [752.7, 581.0, 815.2, 604.1]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [885.0, 581.0, 900.7, 604.1]}, {"text": "414.50", "bbox": [921.6, 581.0, 984.1, 604.1]}, {"text": "Second Quarter  . . . . . . .", "bbox": [360.0, 604.9, 590.4, 628.0]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [716.4, 604.9, 732.0, 628.0]}, {"text": "492.00", "bbox": [752.9, 604.9, 815.3, 628.0]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [885.1, 604.9, 900.7, 628.0]}, {"text": "410.00", "bbox": [921.6, 604.9, 984.0, 628.0]}, {"text": "Third Quarter     . . . . . . .", "bbox": [360.0, 628.9, 573.9, 652.0]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [716.0, 628.9, 731.7, 652.0]}, {"text": "561.00", "bbox": [752.6, 628.9, 815.1, 652.0]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [884.9, 628.9, 900.6, 652.0]}, {"text": "452.75", "bbox": [921.5, 628.9, 984.0, 652.0]}, {"text": "Fourth Quarter   . . . . . . .", "bbox": [360.0, 652.9, 572.8, 676.0]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [716.1, 652.9, 731.8, 676.0]}, {"text": "769.40", "bbox": [752.7, 652.9, 815.2, 676.0]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [885.0, 652.9, 900.7, 676.0]}, {"text": "533.80", "bbox": [921.6, 651.1, 984.5, 676.4]}, {"text": "As of the close of business on February 10, 2006, there were 489 shareholders of record.", "bbox": [210.0, 703.4, 1027.8, 728.7]}, {"text": "We have never paid a cash dividend on our shares of common stock.  In addition, we do not expect", "bbox": [210.0, 748.9, 1124.0, 774.2]}, {"text": "to pay a cash dividend in the foreseeable future as we continue with our objective of increasing shareholder", "bbox": [135.0, 775.2, 1125.1, 800.6]}, {"text": "value by using earnings to fund continued growth in our homebuilding and mortgage banking operations.", "bbox": [135.0, 801.6, 1112.3, 826.9]}, {"text": "We may from time to time repurchase shares of our common stock to also further that objective.  Our bank", "bbox": [135.0, 828.0, 1121.1, 853.3]}, {"text": "indebtedness contains certain restrictive covenants, which limit our ability to pay cash dividends on our", "bbox": [135.0, 854.4, 1089.7, 879.7]}, {"text": "common stock.  See further discussion of the covenants in the Liquidity section of Part II, Item 7 of the", "bbox": [135.0, 880.6, 1087.1, 905.9]}, {"text": "Form 10-K.", "bbox": [135.0, 907.0, 271.8, 932.3]}, {"text": "We had two repurchase authorizations outstanding during the quarter ended December 31, 2005.", "bbox": [210.0, 952.5, 1107.6, 977.8]}, {"text": "On July 28, 2005 (the “July Authorization”) and November 3, 2005 (the “November Authorization”), we", "bbox": [135.0, 978.9, 1103.6, 1004.2]}, {"text": "publicly announced the Board of Director’s approval for us to purchase up to an aggregate of $300 million", "bbox": [135.0, 1005.2, 1117.6, 1030.6]}, {"text": "of our common stock in one or more open market and/or privately negotiated transactions under each of the", "bbox": [135.0, 1031.6, 1127.9, 1056.9]}, {"text": "two authorizations.  Neither the July Authorization nor the November Authorization has an expiration date.", "bbox": [135.0, 1058.0, 1130.5, 1083.3]}, {"text": "During the quarter ended December 31, 2005, we completed the utilization of the July Authorization.  The", "bbox": [135.0, 1084.2, 1116.4, 1109.6]}, {"text": "following table provides information regarding common stock repurchases for the quarter ended December", "bbox": [135.0, 1110.6, 1123.2, 1135.9]}, {"text": "31, 2005:", "bbox": [135.0, 1137.0, 227.5, 1162.3]}, {"text": "Period", "bbox": [215.2, 1336.9, 273.1, 1357.7]}, {"text": "Total Number", "bbox": [405.1, 1286.9, 524.0, 1307.7]}, {"text": "of Shares", "bbox": [424.9, 1311.9, 504.1, 1332.7]}, {"text": "Purchased", "bbox": [420.0, 1336.9, 513.8, 1357.7]}, {"text": "Average", "bbox": [578.8, 1286.9, 650.2, 1307.7]}, {"text": "Price Paid", "bbox": [570.7, 1311.9, 658.3, 1332.7]}, {"text": "per Share", "bbox": [572.8, 1336.9, 656.2, 1357.7]}, {"text": "Total Number of Shares", "bbox": [712.4, 1261.9, 910.4, 1282.7]}, {"text": "Purchased as Part of", "bbox": [726.0, 1286.9, 896.9, 1307.7]}, {"text": "Publicly Announced Plans", "bbox": [703.8, 1311.9, 919.0, 1332.7]}, {"text": "or Programs", "bbox": [758.3, 1336.9, 869.3, 1357.7]}, {"text": "Maximum Number", "bbox": [975.4, 1186.9, 1134.9, 1207.7]}, {"text": "(or Approximate", "bbox": [985.4, 1211.9, 1125.0, 1232.7]}, {"text": "Dollar Value) of", "bbox": [988.3, 1236.9, 1122.2, 1257.7]}, {"text": "Shares That May Yet", "bbox": [967.1, 1261.9, 1143.3, 1282.7]}, {"text": "Be Purchased Under", "bbox": [970.0, 1286.9, 1140.3, 1307.7]}, {"text": "the Plans or Programs", "bbox": [963.0, 1311.9, 1147.4, 1332.7]}, {"text": "(in thousands)", "bbox": [995.8, 1336.9, 1119.2, 1357.7]}, {"text": "October 1-31, 2005(1)", "bbox": [127.5, 1362.7, 300.4, 1383.4]}, {"text": "227,900", "bbox": [431.6, 1362.7, 497.3, 1383.4]}, {"text": "$754.99", "bbox": [581.6, 1362.7, 647.3, 1383.4]}, {"text": "227,900", "bbox": [778.5, 1362.7, 844.2, 1383.4]}, {"text": "$100,833", "bbox": [1017.6, 1362.7, 1097.4, 1383.4]}, {"text": "November 1-30, 2005 (1)", "bbox": [127.5, 1388.7, 324.0, 1409.4]}, {"text": "124,400", "bbox": [431.7, 1388.7, 497.3, 1409.4]}, {"text": "$688.79", "bbox": [581.7, 1388.7, 647.3, 1409.4]}, {"text": "124,400", "bbox": [778.5, 1388.7, 844.2, 1409.4]}, {"text": "$315,148", "bbox": [1017.6, 1388.7, 1097.4, 1409.4]}, {"text": "December 1-31, 2005 (2)", "bbox": [127.5, 1414.7, 321.8, 1435.4]}, {"text": "273,600", "bbox": [431.6, 1414.7, 497.3, 1435.4]}, {"text": "$710.27", "bbox": [581.6, 1414.7, 647.3, 1435.4]}, {"text": "273,600", "bbox": [778.5, 1414.7, 844.2, 1435.4]}, {"text": "$120,818", "bbox": [1017.6, 1414.7, 1092.7, 1435.4]}, {"text": "(1) All shares were purchased under the July Authorization.", "bbox": [172.5, 1440.8, 636.7, 1461.5]}, {"text": "(2) 20,845 shares were purchase under the July Authorization, and 252,755 shares were purchased under the November", "bbox": [172.5, 1465.8, 1084.5, 1486.5]}, {"text": "Authorization.  This fully utilized the July Authorization.  The aggregate $120,818 of our common stock that may yet be", "bbox": [210.0, 1490.8, 1119.9, 1511.5]}, {"text": "purchased relates solely to the November Authorization which was fully utilized in January 2006.", "bbox": [210.0, 1515.8, 947.9, 1536.5]}]}